Description of incident: Holly A. Nordhues CPA notified customers of a data breach when the she discovered a cyberhack to a computer that housed customer information.The information compromised included names, addresses, Social Security number, birthdates, sources of income and tax deductions.She is offering AllClearID for 12 months at no cost. For those affected or questions call 1-877-676-0379.More information: http://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-59137
